00:22:02,319 --> 00:22:03,379
alpha and nothing works?

493
00:22:04,060 --> 00:22:07,942
So remember that your pitch is also an addition.

494
00:22:07,962 --> 00:22:13,584
It is making you, you're showing to the person you're pitching to what sort of person you're

495
00:22:13,604 --> 00:22:14,525
going to be like to work with.

496
00:22:14,965 --> 00:22:17,466
Are you going to be a colleague that they actually want to be involved with?

497
00:22:20,094 --> 00:22:22,675
Number 24, you expect me to know off the bat who you are.

498
00:22:23,556 --> 00:22:24,536
There are a lot of games out there,

499
00:22:24,556 --> 00:22:25,677
and a lot of game developers.

